### Track B — Minimal-Cooler

Use when:
- cooler or ice packs are realistic
- the character packed ahead
- shown foods require cooling
- a better cold meal improves the payoff

### Track C — Hot-Food Optional

Use when:
- thermos or heated lunch gear is realistic
- the scene supports it naturally
- it strengthens contrast
- it still leads back to the PDF system

